Control to unidentified aircraft.

01:46:13.400 --> 01:46:15.868
Unidentified craft, do you copy?

01:46:16.280 --> 01:46:21.479
-Copy that.
-You 're entering restricted airspace.

01:46:22.000 --> 01:46:24.639
-Permission to land!
- You 're off-target. Abort!

01:46:26.600 --> 01:46:28.397
I can't!

